{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, transportation in Hungary in those days, in provincial towns like Pecs-- it wasn't all that interurban.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Transportation was not as it is today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we didn't get together as often as you would do today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But on special occasions, yes, we did, and birthdays and other celebrations and holidays, possibly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did have a-- I had a fairly religious upbringing, in the sense that my household was kosher, strictly kosher.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My late mother kept a kosher household.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I-- the way I remember it, when we were away from home, we would not be strictly kosher.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at home, yes, we would.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, we had Passover dishes and, of course, all the other trappings of kosher households.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's an-- as I mentioned, it's a provincial town in southern Hungary, southwestern Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time-- the time we're talking about, before the war, it had a population of about 75,000.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a university town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I believe it's the first university in Hungary that was established there in the 14th century.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in that sense, it was kind of a cultural center.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a pleasant little town, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- sort of next to a mountain range, which probably in Canada would be called hills, but in, in Hungary, it was a mountain.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and it was, yeah, pleasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The climate was quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was fairly warm-- not Mediterranean, but moderate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community before the war, I believe, was numbered about 4,500 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] out of a population, as I said, about 75,000.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it wasn't a very large Jewish, you know, community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was fairly well off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My, my own family-- my father was certainly middle-class.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
